IT MIGHT BE A POLAR VORTEX OUT THERE, BUT CHINOOK BLAST IS BACK WITH THE HEAT! 🔥

From light installations, to the @fourwindsyyc Indigenous Showcase & Market founded by @tonytoosick, this weekend you can shop 'til you drop and even take in a fashion show featuring nationally respected Indigenous designers and artists.

Catch the free, family fun Friday January 27th, until January 29th at the Municipal Complex Atrium.

@chinookblast is here until February 12. It’s going to be Snow. Much. Fun!

